PDB Path Mismatch

PDB Path mismatch: <Project Path>

Serena ChangeMan Builder found a mismatch between the .PDB path in the saved build job and the .PDB path of the selected project. One possible reason for this would be if you ran a build job in one of the Serena ChangeMan Builder integrated clients, then copied the .TGT file from that Serena ChangeMan Version Manager project to another Version Manager project.
